            <li><strong>Final Academic Status:</strong> This will indicate whether you have 'Passed', 'Failed', or have been awarded a 'Supplementary' (SUPP).</li>
            <li><strong>Common Abbreviations Encountered:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>RW:</strong> Result Withheld (often due to missing previous year records or technical discrepancies).</li>
                    <li><strong>INC:</strong> Incomplete (missing practical or internal marks for the 2024 session).</li>
                    <li><strong>RL:</strong> Result Later (marks are pending but the university will update them shortly).</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>

